<!--to create a drop down menu, we use the select tags give it a name and an id. in the drop down menu, you will have options, so simply 
just use the option tagse here inside of the first option tag give it a value specfic to its meaning, as it will be called on by another 
web technology -->
            <select name="shipping" id="shipping">       
                <option value="7 day shipping">Free 7 Day Shipping</option>
                <option value="2 day shipping">2 Day Shipping</option>
                <option value="overnight shipping">Overnight Shipping</option>
